David Garrison https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/David_Garrison 0 David Earl Garrison (born June 30, 1952) is an American actor. His primary venue is live theatre, but he is best known as the character Steve Rhoades in the television series, Married... with Children. He also appeared in numerous theatrical plays, particularly that of The Wizard on Broadway and in many tours of the musical, Wicked. David_Earl_Garrison ( born June_30_,_1952 ) is an_American_actor .
